description: Get a list of available geographical regions.

sku.description: Name of SKU used to filter the regions.

xenon_workers_enabled.description: Specify true if you want to filter to only regions that support Xenon workers.

linux_workers_enabled.description: Specify true if you want to filter to only regions that support Linux workers.

linux_dynamic_workers_enabled.description: Specify true if you want to filter to only regions that support Linux Consumption Workers.

subscription_id.description: Your Azure subscription ID. This is a GUID-formatted string (e.g. 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000).
